## 7️⃣ Environment Variables for API URL

```bash
# .env.local
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:5000   # Development
# Production: NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com
```

```javascript
const baseURL = process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL
```

